[color=Gray]This application is to be submitted to the Head of Security for review. If no Head of Security is available, the Captain or a member of Central Command can review this application in their stead. Once this application has been approved and stamped by one of the individuals previously stated, this form should be taken to the Head of Personnel to process. Either the Head of Security, Captain, or a Central Command Official will need to assist in processing this form. This form is only valid when stamped by the Head of Personnel and either the Head of Security or the Captain. A Central Command stamp alone can also validate this form.[/color]
